cu.explanation_en: Setting drb_ciphering to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing errors and prevent the gNB from starting properly.

du.explanation_en: Setting drb_ciphering to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing errors and prevent the gNB from starting properly.
du.explanation_zh: 將 drb_ciphering 設定為無效值 'invalid' 會導致配置解析錯誤，並阻止 gNB 正確啟動。
